742
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:49,440
"Sorry that I can't help much," says Ricki.

743
00:38:49,440 --> 00:38:50,760
"Hey, don't worry.

744
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:55,400
You have to rest so you can get better 
quickly, then you can play basketball again."

745
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:57,440
The doorbell rings.

746
00:38:58,240 --> 00:38:58,760
"Oh!

747
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:01,520
Here is our first guest!" says Ricki.

748
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:03,000
"I want to answer the door.

749
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:05,320
Remember our plan, everybody."

750
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,480
The others nod.

751
00:39:06,480 --> 00:39:11,320
They are going to try and find out about Caper 
by talking to the players during the party.

752
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:16,680
They need to know who is jealous of Ricki 
and Tony and who drives a red Subaru.

753
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:20,320
They also need to find out who uses e-mail a lot.

754
00:39:20,320 --> 00:39:24,560
Could the name "Caper" be 
a code word for something?

755
00:39:24,560 --> 00:39:27,120
The friends all feel excited and tense.

756
00:39:27,120 --> 00:39:31,440
What's going to happen tonight?

757
00:39:31,440 --> 00:39:35,200
Two of the basketball players 
from the team are at the door.

758
00:39:35,200 --> 00:39:37,240
"Hi, Ricki!" says Anthony.

759
00:39:37,240 --> 00:39:38,240
"Good to see you.

760
00:39:38,240 --> 00:39:39,360
How are you?

761
00:39:39,360 --> 00:39:41,000
We miss you at practice."

762
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:46,200
"I miss it too, but Tony always 
tells me about it," replies Ricki.

763
00:39:46,200 --> 00:39:47,800
"You guys work hard!

764
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:49,680
The party's out back in the yard.

765
00:39:49,680 --> 00:39:54,680
Have fun!" Later Stacy is talking 
to Ricki when the bell rings again.

766
00:39:54,680 --> 00:39:55,800
"Oh, hi, Pat.

767
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:56,920
Hi, Kyle," says Ricki.

768
00:39:56,920 --> 00:39:58,240
"Nice to see you!

769
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:01,000
Come in - the party's in the yard."

770
00:40:01,000 --> 00:40:02,440
"Thanks, Anderson.

771
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:05,200
We're here with Eric Caplin and John Roberts."

772
00:40:05,200 --> 00:40:08,960
"I don't see them," says Stacy, 
looking out into the street.

773
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,800
"Where are they?"

774
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:14,400
"Oh, they're parking the car," 
replies Pat, looking away.

775
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:18,400
"In the next street?" asks Stacy, incredulously.

776
00:40:18,400 --> 00:40:19,360
"Oh, umm...

777
00:40:19,360 --> 00:40:24,720
Eric's car makes a lot of noise, so he's parking 
it in the next street," replies Kyle quickly.

778
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:27,520
"He doesn't want to annoy your neighbors."

779
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:30,960
"That doesn't sound like Eric 
Caplin at all," thinks Stacy.

780
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:34,440
"He's not usually so considerate!"

781
00:40:34,440 --> 00:40:38,320
Eric and John arrive soon after 
and join the rest of the party.

782
00:40:38,320 --> 00:40:42,280
The music is playing loudly and 
a lot of people are dancing.

783
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:46,720
Trish notices Eric and Pat talking 
together in a dark corner of the garden.

784
00:40:46,720 --> 00:40:49,880
She looks around to see if anyone is watching her,  

785
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:54,080
then goes around the trees behind 
them so that they can't see her.

786
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:56,560
She goes nearer and listens to them.

787
00:40:56,560 --> 00:40:59,400
"They don't suspect anything," Eric is saying.

788
00:40:59,400 --> 00:41:01,000
"They're too stupid."

789
00:41:01,000 --> 00:41:03,720
"Well, it was a risk to bring the car tonight.

790
00:41:03,720 --> 00:41:07,200
That wasn't clever, Eric," replies Pat.

791
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:09,520
"I parked it in the next street so they can't see  

792
00:41:09,520 --> 00:41:12,560
it and the mechanic is going 
