00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,440
We could get into trouble."

796
00:41:19,440 --> 00:41:20,840
Pat is nervous.

797
00:41:20,840 --> 00:41:22,800
"Hey, don't worry, Pat.

798
00:41:22,800 --> 00:41:29,720
Anderson isn't going to play basketball again, and 
we're going to stop Caruso, too," replies Eric.

799
00:41:29,720 --> 00:41:30,480
"Mmm.

800
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:34,480
Let's go back to the party before 
someone notices us," Pat says.

801
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:38,040
Trish quietly comes out of the 
shadows and goes over to Tony.

802
00:41:38,040 --> 00:41:39,160
"Tony, quick!

803
00:41:39,160 --> 00:41:42,720
Get Stacy and Ricki and meet me 
in Ricki's room in five minutes.

804
00:41:42,720 --> 00:41:45,640
I have something important to tell all of you."

805
00:41:45,640 --> 00:41:50,120
The four friends are sitting on Ricki's 
bed looking expectantly at Trish.

806
00:41:50,120 --> 00:41:52,920
"What is it, Trish?" asks Stacy.

807
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:57,240
"I think I know who the driver of 
the red car is!" replies her friend.

808
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:59,800
"Who?" asks Ricki.

809
00:41:59,800 --> 00:42:01,320
"Eric Caplin.

810
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:04,040
Now he wants to stop Tony too."

811
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:05,680
Tony's face is white.

812
00:42:05,680 --> 00:42:08,640
"How do you know that, Trish?" he asks.

813
00:42:08,640 --> 00:42:10,680
"I heard them talking in the garden.

814
00:42:10,680 --> 00:42:12,680
They didn't see me," she explains.

815
00:42:12,680 --> 00:42:16,640
"What are we going to do now?" asks Stacy, afraid.

816
00:42:16,640 --> 00:42:19,120
"I don't know yet," replies Ricki.

817
00:42:19,120 --> 00:42:22,640
"Let's go back to the party before 
they notice we're not there.

818
00:42:22,640 --> 00:42:25,080
Perhaps we can catch them 
out if they think we don't  

819
00:42:25,080 --> 00:42:27,120
know anything."
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 

