00:44:21,560 --> 00:44:24,720
'Caper' is Eric's user name on the computer.

857
00:44:24,720 --> 00:44:28,280
He uses the initial parts of 
his name for his user name.

858
00:44:28,280 --> 00:44:31,320
In this case the first three 
letters of his last name,  

859
00:44:31,320 --> 00:44:35,880
